timing_report...eshold_scaling(25.10)    timing_report...eshold_scaling(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_drv_enable_slew_threshold_scaling

Syntax
       timing_report_drv_enable_slew_threshold_scaling {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables  the  transition  constraints scaling as per the slew threshold
       value.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

